{"tid":2064301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【615一周年重溫】林鄭：暫緩修訂逃犯條例　金鐘衝突為「暴動」　警方執法「天公地義」","createTime":"2020-06-14T16:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T16:39:11.000Z","uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e528fc6439494fda888fc7f20b95fd800570efc8","tid":2064301,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:39:11.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥宣布，暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》的工作，林鄭月娥說，建制派議員及社會各界領袖近日都公開或私下向她表示，應該停一停、想一想，不應恢復二讀草案，對社會造成更大衝擊，加上台灣表示絕不接受在特區政府建議安排下移交台灣殺人案疑犯，令草案在今個立法年度通過的迫切性已不復存在。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463028-20190615.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463028-20190615.htm&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8l8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=85284c00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463028-20190615.htm&h=c353925f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463028-20190615.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n在記者會上，行政長官林鄭月娥多次被問到，是否須為事件問責下台。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥未有直接回應，表示以成為公僕為榮，又否認事件令中央政府添煩添亂。<br />\n<br />\n對於星期三發生的金鐘衝突，林鄭月娥稱，同意警方將事件定性為「暴動」，形容警方執法「天公地義」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463062-20190615.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463062-20190615.htm&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8l8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=1b5a37d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463062-20190615.htm&h=fad79a00\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463062-20190615.htm</a>"}]}